dataset_id: Woody Biomass for Eastern U.S. Forests, 1983-1996
title: Woody Biomass for Eastern U.S. Forests, 1983-1996
summary: Estimates of the woody biomass density and pools were derived at the county scale of resolution of all forests of the eastern United States using new approaches for converting inventoried wood volume to estimates of above and belowground biomass.
